body:
This PR makes a number of changes to clarify control flow; multiple instances like:
```
for(...) {
    if (!cond)
        continue;
    //...
}
```

into the clearer:
```
for(...) {
    if (cond) {
        //...
    }
}
```

It also changes a loop like:
```
for (auto wire : module->wires()) {
    if (!wire->port_input)
        continue;
    //...
}
```

into the more efficient:
```
for (auto id : module->ports) {
    RTLIL::Wire *wire = module->wire(id);
    if (wire->port_input) {
        //...
    }
}
```


The PR is split into three commits for easier review, but I am happy to rebase this into one commit if preferred.

